{"tid":2103238,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【整合】【初選懶人包+QNA】銀髮族冇電話都可以投","createTime":"2020-07-11T05:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T07:58:34.000Z","uid":24331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b811b6021a4f9ce12d4b9d40679a64512b0894","tid":2103238,"uid":24331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"1. 邊度搵到票站？<br />\n<a href=\"https://legco2020.vote4.hk/primaries/stations/HKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.vote4.hk%2Fprimaries%2Fstations%2FHKI&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyL0p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=c287bcf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.vote4.hk/primaries/stations/HKI</a><br />\n你選區 (港島/九東/九西/新東/新西) 入面所有票站都去得<br />\n<br />\n2. 我要帶啲咩去投票？<br />\n(1) 身份證 + (2) 住址證明 - 包括水電煤電話單、銀行信、住戶證等等 (文本、電子版本、截圖 及相片皆接納)<br />\n選民登記網站 Cap Screen唔用得<br />\n<br />\n3. 投票過程係點？<br />\n1) Scan 票站既QR CODE<br />\n2) IOS 直接用網站投票 Android好似要down app (聽現場票站義工講既)<br />\n3) 入返票站嘅四位數編號<br />\n4) 係咪傳統界別嘅選民 (e.g. 鄉議局/漁農界/保險界/航運交通界/教育界/法律界/會計界/醫學界/衞生服務界/工程界/建築、測量 、都巿規劃及園境界/勞工界/社會福利界/地產及建造界/旅遊界/商界 /工業界/金融界/金融服務界/體育、演藝、文化及出版界/進出口界 /紡織及製衣界 /批發及零售界 /資訊科技界 /飲食界 <br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">係以上界別嘅選民就撳是 只要你要投超級區議會或者唔係以上界別就撳否</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxDbjYO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxDbjYO.jpg&h=689cc78e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5) 填返身份證號碼 出生日期同埋身份證簽發日期等資料<br />\n6) 選擇你心儀嘅代議士<br />\n7) 拎住網站嘅QR CODE進入票站比職員scan 同埋出示返身份證同埋住址證明文件就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n4. 唔小心撳左昆 冇得投超級區議會咁點算？<br />\n重新scan過個QR CODE重新做多次以上流程就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n5. 銀髮族冇電話可唔可以投票<br />\n票站內嘅義工好似會有電話幫啲銀髮族投票<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">多謝各位巴打嘅資料 如果大家喺票站見到啲銀髮族阿叔師奶唔識嘅麻煩過去幫下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為好多票站義工都柒下柒下咁 有錯請更正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"66bc5a963c0ff5687f444368bec482f51e30f328","tid":2103238,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7ca0cc962ab69def203919338257b36114a11645","tid":2103238,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43129e84482a5a01b4c5e1e73ade6e20b4825227","tid":2103238,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d82cf19a28c7721deec18ab156b245f525e8141","tid":2103238,"uid":24331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:16:09.000Z","msg":"【整合】【初選懶人包+QNA】銀髮族冇電話都可以投<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2103243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2103243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推另一個post 依個打錯字"},{"pid":"4719f661557f7205b41e48465cb4b383f3a5ef16","tid":2103238,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:28:08.000Z","msg":"7月11,12日（六，日）<br />\n0900-2100<br />\n去票站投票<br />\n<br />\n無論你點投, 投比邊個<br />\n<br />\n撳入呢度揀你個地區，有埋地圖帶你去票站<br />\n<a href=\"https://legco2020.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.com%2F&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyL0p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=ba47fd23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n民意嘅展現永遠係最有效嘅抗爭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5963d1d652ae5df68b941f5b53a5270eb66ddc","tid":2103238,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T08:10:38.000Z","msg":"7月11,12日（六，日）<br />\n0900-2100<br />\n去票站投票<br />\n<br />\n無論你點投, 投比邊個<br />\n<br />\n民意嘅展現永遠係最有效嘅抗爭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n=================<br />\n<br />\n撳入呢度揀你個地區，有埋地圖帶你去票站<br />\n<a href=\"https://legco2020.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.com%2F&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2B